      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that needs a little TLC. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car is roadworthy, there are visible signs of wear including some minor exterior scratches and thinning paint. The interior shows its age with some upholstery wear, and you can expect to perform some routine maintenance soon, such as replacing the brake pads and tires. It's a dependable car that just needs some cosmetic and minor mechanical attention to bring it back to its best.",
