    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for me\u2014honestly, it's a total joy to drive! It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more adventures on the road. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great, this is the one for you. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take a look, and see why I\u2019ve enjoyed it so much!",
