    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This performance-oriented machine features a high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant paired with a precision-gated manual transmission. The drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power through a mechanical limited-slip differential that ensures optimal traction during lateral load transfers. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system refresh and the installation of poly-composite bushings to maintain communicative steering rack feedback and chassis rigidity. While the aesthetic reflects honest use consistent with its 'good' status, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all cylinders and synchronized gear shifts\u2014are exceptional. It is a technically sound example for the purist who demands tactile throttle response and a balanced power-to-weight ratio.",
