    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a well-cared-for 2017 BMW M2 finished in Alpine White over a Black Dakota leather interior with signature blue stitching. This vehicle has been driven thoughtfully and maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep shine, though close inspection will reveal minor peppering of stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear quarter panel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The factory 19-inch Style 437M wheels are in great shape with only a hint of curb rash on the passenger rear. Inside, the cabin is a pristine environment; the leather bolsters remain firm, the carbon fiber trim is free of delamination, and all electronics, including the iDrive system and Harman Kardon audio, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It features a comprehensive service log, with the most recent oil service and spark plug replacement performed just 1,500 miles ago. The N55 engine runs smoothly without any leaks, and the dual-clutch transmission shifts with precision. This is a turn-key enthusiast car ready for its next chapter.",
