    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to hit the road! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you\u2019re getting a great vehicle that still has tons of life left in it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
