    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline via individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior lateral traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high-load cornering. Equipped with a refined MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry and ventilated compound rotors, this chassis offers exceptional feedback and thermal management. A mechanically sorted machine optimized for high-performance driving.",
